CAMPECHE , Mexico | Mon <TIMEX3 tid="t2" type="DATE" value="2010-06-28">Jun 28 , 2010</TIMEX3> <TIMEX3 tid="t5" type="TIME" value="2010-06-28T16:11">4:11 pm</TIMEX3> EDT CAMPECHE , Mexico -LRB- Reuters -RRB- - Tropical storm Alex was set to become a hurricane on <TIMEX3 tid="t4" type="DATE" value="2010-06-22">Tuesday</TIMEX3> , delaying BP Plc 's efforts to increase siphoning capacity at the gushing oil leak in the Gulf of Mexico while some companies pulled workers from the area .
