` ` Some strengthening is forecast during <TIMEX3 tid="t17" type="DURATION" value="PXD">the next couple of days</TIMEX3> and Alex is expected to become a hurricane on <TIMEX3 tid="t16" type="DATE" value="2010-06-22">Tuesday</TIMEX3> , '' the U.S. National Hurricane Center said on its latest update .
